reviews.text: I had the tsukemen. Broth is quite fishy one and a bit too thin for my liking. Speed and service were all fine, except the raw egg cafe as we were half way through.  Spicy sauce not very spicy, noodles were tasty.

Expensive and gave me a bad stomach ache. Soup base very salty and noodles too hard, they only gave one slice of pork... Poor quality. Would never go back after the bad stomach ache I got after dinner.
Here is one of my favorite ramen restaurant in HK.Good taste and reasonable.

A good choice for ramen in the Taikoo Shing area. The store is small and seats around 20 people at max capacity so during lunch hours there will be a queue. The Tsukemen ramen here is what you want to order here. 

Food: 4 stars
Value: 3.5 stars
Overall: 3.75 stars
Recommendations: Taukemen ramen, fried chicken

They do a pretty good job with the ramen here. The noodles have a nice texture and absorb well the dipping sauce. The soup base is a tad salty but I find tsukemen typically on the salty side since the soup is concentrated. I wouldn’t drink the soup base unless you add some water as instructed. 

The base ramen will run you between 65-100 hkd depending on what you order and with the add ons I would definitely expect to pay over 120 hkd for a bowl of ramen. You have the choice of how you want your noodles cooked, the amount of noodles, and whether or not you want green onions. Worth stoping by if you are in the area.
Small Japanese restaurant, but tasty noodles, I ate two orders. Excellent job!

reviews.text: I had the tsukemen. Broth is quite fishy one and a bit too thin for my liking. Speed and service were all fine, except the raw egg cafe as we were half way through.  Spicy sauce not very spicy, noodles were tasty.

Expensive and gave me a bad stomach ache. Soup base very salty and noodles too hard, they only gave one slice of pork... Poor quality. Would never go back after the bad stomach ache I got after dinner.
個沾汁味道夠濃,但湯完全唔夠熱, 上嗰陣已經係暖, 食一陣即刻凍曬, 雖然沾汁夠濃,但麵唔掛湯,食嗰陣冇乜味,個湯真心唔錯,但敗筆在於整體加埋唔掂😔
有沾麵同拉麵可供選擇。另有，各款小食（餃子及炸雞之類）,還有炒飯。而今次我食的這個拉麵是他們的特製拉麵，很濃厚的湯汁及勁大塊的叉燒，並配有溏心蛋，走過附近可以幫襯試一試。
湯太浠，沾不上面，跟日本有距離。
